// reason.fsb — reasoning / entailment commands (NEW word-based syntax).
// Commands: |= (per-atom brave-consequence check; verbose, computes per atom),
//           |= %  (cautious consequences = landmarks),
//           |= %% (atoms not in any AS = impossibles).
// Note: |= keeps its symbol; % / %% here are sub-flags to |=, not the sig command.
|= %
|= %%
|=
:q
